- TPD ternary (PROTAC + molecular glue) — three-body binding 의 quantum advantage
- AAV capsid engineering — protein-protein assembly + capsid surface
- protein-protein interaction (menin-KMT2A, sFlt-1, IL-6R) — interface scoring
- receptor allosteric pocket (asciminib STAMP, mavacamten, deucravacitinib) — non-orthosteric pocket VQE
- KRAS G12C/D/V covalent + selectivity ranking
- BCL-2/BCL-XL platelet selectivity (venetoclax + navitoclax)

### 4B. 2차 (보조 fit) — 양자-VQE 가 보조 layer

- peptide design (cyclic + macrocycle + stapled) — moderate-size molecule VQE
- RNA secondary structure (ASO + miRNA + ribozyme) — RNA-ligand scoring
- 비공유 binding (allosteric inhibitor + cryptic pocket) — pocket prediction + ranking
- bispecific Fab geometry — paratope geometric fit
- nanoparticle surface ligand density (LNP + GalNAc)

### 4C. 3차 (한정 fit) — 양자-VQE 외부 modality

- policy + ethics + DTx — modality 외부, 양자 적용 한정
- AI imaging + radiomics — ML-pipeline 별도, quantum advantage 한정
- behavioral + addiction + DTx — non-pharmacological, modality 외부
